  |- wceq(cinag, cmpt(s0, universe, copab(s1, s2, wa(wa(wcel(cv(s1), cfv(cbs, cv(s0))), wcel(cv(s2), co(cfv(cbs, cv(s0)), cmap, co(nat0, cfzo, nat3)))), wa(w3a(wne(cfv(cv(s2), nat0), cfv(cv(s2), nat1)), wne(cfv(cv(s2), nat2), cfv(cv(s2), nat1)), wne(cv(s1), cfv(cv(s2), nat1))), wrex(s3, cfv(cbs, cv(s0)), wa(wcel(cv(s3), co(cfv(cv(s2), nat0), cfv(citv, cv(s0)), cfv(cv(s2), nat2))), wo(wceq(cv(s3), cfv(cv(s2), nat1)), wbr(cv(s3), cfv(cfv(chlg, cv(s0)), cfv(cv(s2), nat1)), cv(s1))))))))))
  -| diffss(s0, s1)
  -| diffss(s0, s2)
  -| diffss(s0, s3)

}

blocks.origin:
thm inagne3(class c0, class c1, class c2, class c3, class c4, class c5, class c6, class c7, wff w0) {
  |- wi(w0, wne(c0, c1))
  -| wceq(c2, cfv(cbs, c3))
  -| wceq(c4, cfv(citv, c3))
  -| wceq(c5, cfv(chlg, c3))
  -| wi(w0, wcel(c0, c2))
  -| wi(w0, wcel(c6, c2))
  -| wi(w0, wcel(c1, c2))
  -| wi(w0, wcel(c7, c2))
  -| wi(w0, wcel(c3, cstrkg))
  -| wi(w0, wbr(c0, cfv(cinag, c3), cs3(c6, c1, c7)))
} = {
  simp3d(w0, wne(c0, c1), wne(c6, c1), wne(c7, c1))
  simpld(w0, w3a(wne(c6, c1), wne(c7, c1), wne(c0, c1)), wrex(hs0, c2, wa(wcel(cv(hs0), co(c6, c4, c7)), wo(wceq(cv(hs0), c1), wbr(cv(hs0), cfv(c5, c1), c0)))))
  mpbid(w0, wa(w3a(wne(c6, c1), wne(c7, c1), wne(c0, c1)), wrex(hs0, c2, wa(wcel(cv(hs0), co(c6, c4, c7)), wo(wceq(cv(hs0), c1), wbr(cv(hs0), cfv(c5, c1), c0))))), wbr(c0, cfv(cinag, c3), cs3(c6, c1, c7)))
  isinag(hs0, c0, c3, c6, c1, c7, c2, c4, c5, cstrkg, w0)
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
  diff.hs0.c(c3)
  diff.hs0.c(c6)
  diff.hs0.c(c1)
  diff.hs0.c(c7)
  diff.hs0.c(c2)
  diff.hs0.w(w0)
}

thm inagne3(class c0, class c1, class c2, class c3, class c4, class c5, class c6, class c7, wff w0) {
  ‚ä¢ (w0 ‚Üí c0 ‚â† c1)
  ‚ä£ c2 =(Base ` c3)
  ‚ä£ c4 =(Itv ` c3)
  ‚ä£ c5 =(hlG ` c3)
  ‚ä£ (w0 ‚Üí c0 ‚àà c2)
  ‚ä£ (w0 ‚Üí c6 ‚àà c2)
  ‚ä£ (w0 ‚Üí c1 ‚àà c2)
  ‚ä£ (w0 ‚Üí c7 ‚àà c2)
  ‚ä£ (w0 ‚Üí c3 ‚àà TarskiG)
  ‚ä£ (w0 ‚Üí c0[(inA ` c3)]<" c6 . c1 . c7 ">)
} = {
  simp3d(w0, c0 ‚â† c1, c6 ‚â† c1, c7 ‚â† c1)
  simpld(w0, (c6 ‚â† c1 ‚àß c7 ‚â† c1 ‚àß c0 ‚â† c1), ‚àÉ(hs0 ‚àà c2,(hs0 ‚àà(c6[c4]c7)‚àß(hs0 = c1 ‚à® hs0[(c5 ` c1)]c0))))
  mpbid(w0, ((c6 ‚â† c1 ‚àß c7 ‚â† c1 ‚àß c0 ‚â† c1)‚àß ‚àÉ(hs0 ‚àà c2,(hs0 ‚àà(c6[c4]c7)‚àß(hs0 = c1 ‚à® hs0[(c5 ` c1)]c0)))), c0[(inA ` c3)]<" c6 . c1 . c7 ">)
  isinag(hs0, c0, c3, c6, c1, c7, c2, c4, c5, cstrkg, w0)
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
  diff.hs0.c(c3)
  diff.hs0.c(c6)
  diff.hs0.c(c1)
  diff.hs0.c(c7)
  diff.hs0.c(c2)
  diff.hs0.w(w0)
}
